div.head: Description of changes for 2012.06
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft that has been copied from a transcription of the Reims manuscript. It awaits corrections and additions pending a collation comparision of manuscript witnesses. Citations, cross-references, and a critical apparatus still await construction.
